      "Implemented secure communication, cryptography and hardened JWT-based authentication.",
      "Built CI/CD pipelines with automated validation, static analysis and security controls."
    ],
    type: "professional",
    skills: ["Architecture", "Node.js", "Angular", "JWT", "Cryptography", "CI/CD", "Secure Engineering"]
  },
  {
    title: "Software Engineer I",
    company: "Serkes Consulting",
    period: "Jul 2025 – Nov 2025",
    description: [
      "Developed a secure RESTful API with OAuth/OIDC and role-based authorization.",
      "Built a modular Angular frontend with reactive communication patterns.",
      "Containerized and deployed the platform using secure Docker practices."
    ],
    type: "professional",
    skills: ["Express.js", "Angular", "OAuth 2.0", "OIDC", "RBAC", "Docker"]
  },
  {
    title: "Part-Time Software Professor",
    company: "National University of Costa Rica",
    period: "Jun 2024 – Nov 2025",
    description: [
      "Tutored students in advanced data structures and algorithmic fundamentals.",
      "Guided programming projects using C++, Python and Java."
    ],
    type: "professional",
    skills: ["C++", "Python", "Java", "Data Structures", "Algorithms"]
  },
  {
    title: "Systems Engineer",
    company: "SINART Digital",
    period: "Feb 2024 – Jun 2025",
    description: [
      "Developed a scalable billing platform using Laravel, Vue.js and MySQL.",
      "Managed CI/CD workflows, automated tests and secure deployments on Ubuntu.",
      "Hardened infrastructure through container security, WAF rules and RBAC policies."
    ],
    type: "professional",
    skills: ["Laravel", "Vue.js", "MySQL", "CI/CD", "Docker", "Terraform", "Security Hardening"]
  },
  {
    title: "Academic Mentor",
    company: "National University of Costa Rica",
    period: "Feb 2023 – Present",
